&gt;&gt; Amalia Castaneda:
My favorite part

00:00:25.390 --> 00:00:29.090
of being a Junior Fellow I think
is just access to the resource

00:00:29.090 --> 00:00:33.380
of the Library, from lectures, to
the people here at the Library,

00:00:33.380 --> 00:00:37.090
having the chance to pick the
brains of curators and specialists.

00:00:37.090 --> 00:00:39.450
And also sort of mingling
among other fellows

00:00:39.450 --> 00:00:42.360
that will also be specialists
in their field one day.

00:00:42.360 --> 00:00:44.900
So I think having access to that
network is my favorite part.

