for a couple of years

00:02:04.780 --> 00:02:08.290
but just never really opened my
eyes to the depth of material

00:02:08.290 --> 00:02:10.870
that the library has and the level
of accessibility that there is.

00:02:10.870 --> 00:02:13.760
&gt;&gt; Jessica Abbazio: So I would
just advise future Junior Fellows

00:02:13.760 --> 00:02:16.600
to take advantage of everything
there is available in D.C. This is

00:02:16.600 --> 00:02:19.250
such a rich cultural area
that there's so many things

00:02:19.250 --> 00:02:21.060
that you can learn, and do,
and see while you're here.

00:02:21.060 --> 00:02:22.880
So absolutely try to do that.

00:02:22.880 --> 00:02:24.180
&gt;&gt; Amalia Castaneda: I'll
be motivating more people

00:02:24.180 --> 00:02:26.270
